data.description: **$5K Seller Concession** Welcome to this stunning home located in this highly sought-after neighborhood! Boasting an open-concept floor plan, this home offers a seamless flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating a spacious and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen features exquisite granite countertops, adding elegance and functionality to the heart of the home. With four bedrooms and two bathrooms, there is ample space for a growing family or guests. Additionally, this home includes a versatile flex space that can be used as a home office, playroom, or gym, catering to your specific needs and preferences. The extended covered patio helps you keep cool while enjoying evenings in the backyard. The community offers fantastic amenities such as sparkling pools, scenic trails, and beautiful parks, perfect for enjoying outdoor activities and fostering a sense of community. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own! **New Roof - June 2023 **Foundation repair - June 2023**
